data.title: All About Your Local Hometown San Diego Nissan Dealership Mossy
data.meta_description: When you're in the market for a Nissan for sale, Mossy Nissan is your hometown, San Diego dealership. With seven locations in the area, there's one near you.
data.text:
Mossy Nissan has been serving the San Diego community since 1982! Mossy is the premiere San Diego Nissan car dealer with 7 convenient locations to serve you; Chula Vista, El Cajon, Escondido, Kearny Mesa, National City, Oceanside and Poway.

Mossy Nissan has a LARGE selection of new Nissans and quality used vehicles in San Diego. Mossy Nissan offers vehicles with better quality, better safety features and better innovation. So call us today or come see us in person! We have seven convenient locations to choose from: Chula Vista, El Cajon, Escondido, Kearny Mesa, National City, Oceanside and Poway!

Mossy Nissan, Your New and Used Nissan Dealer in San Diego!

While you're visiting our website, take a look at our online inventory of new and pre-owned Nissan vehicles, including the Nissan Sentra, Altima, Maxima, Versa, Rogue and Murano for the San Diego region. Mossy Nissan is a leading provider of Nissans to San Diego thanks to our quality automobiles and superior sales staff. We encourage you to come and visit us at any of our seven locations in San Diego to view our selection in person, speak to a sales professional or take an Altima, Maxima, Versa, Rogue or Sentra for a test drive. Call us if you have any questions about any Nissan vehicle.

USED CARS

Looking for great deals on reliable used cars? Skip Carmax and AutoTrader, come to Mossy Nissan! We have the San Diego used car with great fuel economy that you have been searching for and we can give you a great price in relation to Kelley Blue Book with low car payments! With a variety of cars, trucks, SUVs and fuel efficient hybrids to choose from and an experienced sales team, we are confident that we can find the vehicle that was built for you. On our San Diego used car lot we feature vehicles by many of today's top automakers, including fuel efficient San Diego used cars like the Honda Civic, Honda Accord, Toyota Tacoma, Toyota Corolla, Toyota Camry, Hyundai Elantra, Hyundai Sonata, Audi A4, BMW 325, Dodge Charger, Jeep Cherokee, Jeep Wrangler, KIA Optima, KIA Soul, KIA Sportage, KIA Sorento, KIA Forte, Ford Focus, Ford Explorer, Ford F150, Ford Ranger, Ford Mustang and many more reliable San Diego used cars! We also offer a huge selection of safe, reliable Nissan used cars, like the Nissan Altima, Nissan Sentra, Nissan Maxima, Nissan Frontier, Nissan Versa, Nissan Titan, Nissan Pathfinder, Nissan Rogue, Nissan 350z and Nissan 370z. Each and every one of our safe, reliable San Diego used cars has been through a detailed inspection by our auto mechanics so you can be sure that we only stock the highest quality used vehicles. And each used car comes with a CarFax report! Want to sell your car? Give Mossy Nissan the opportunity to make a free quote for your trade-in! You can sell your car to Mossy Nissan with no obligation to buy!

EASY FINANCING

Whether you are leasing or financing a new or used car, Mossy Nissan is here to get you into the driver's seat with low car payments you can afford. Our finance specialists are committed to helping you secure a car loan in the San Diego region. No matter what your current credit is, stop by or call to speak with our friendly Mossy Nissan salespeople.

SERVICE, PARTS, & ACCESSORIES

You can get original Nissan Car Parts and professional car repairs from the experts at Mossy Nissan. If you're looking for vehicle maintenance, repairs or parts in the San Diego region, visit our dealership for the professional service you deserve. We're located at 7 Locations in San Diego, or you can call us if you have any questions.

COMMUNITY INVOLVEMENT

Our dealership is always ready and eager to give back to the community by participating in local events and giving back to organizations in our neighborhood and surrounding cities. Through donations and contributions to special programs, we support the local businesses and families around us.

We hope to see you soon! You can call Mossy Nissan at (888) 50-MOSSY, or come visit us in person. We're conveniently located at 7 locations in San Diego, CA and we look forward to helping you with your automotive needs.
